snippet.description:
Vikas ‡§ú‡•Ä ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§§‡§∞‡§π ‡§Ö‡§™‡§®‡•á Skills, ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§®‡§§, ‡§ú‡§º‡§ø‡§¶ ‡§î‡§∞ ‡§ú‡•Å‡§®‡•Ç‡§® ‡§ï‡•á ‡§¶‡§Æ ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§¨‡§®‡•á‡§Ç Successful :https://joshskills.app.link/4iaNjbgiVwb

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti‚Äôs professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 01 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. Why Vikas Sir's surname is Dvyakirti?
2. What was his UPSC Exam Result?
3. How Dr. Vikas Divyakirti handles Drishti IAS and what is his role?
4. What is Dr. Vikas Divyakirti's ideology regarding Anxiety and Depression?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

snippet.title: SYAAPA : EP 02 | LADKI KA CHAKAR | KANGRA BOYS
snippet.description:
"SYAAPA" is Himachal's First Ever web series produced by KANGRA BOYS

"SYAAPA" is the story of four friends and one of their senior advocate Makkhan. In this episode all four friends after being expelled from their college return to their ancestral house in their village. Here they encounter a dead body in their house and all of them are haunted by the fear that they might be accused of his murder. Now, they call one of their college senior advocate Makhan for help. Let's see how these four friends deal with this problem and if advocate Makkhan comes to help them.

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Sadhguru X Kamiya Jani | Sunday Brunch EP 95 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this episode of Sunday Brunch we caught up with the spiritual leader, Sadhguru at Isha Yoga Center, Coimbatore. He is the founder and head of the Isha Foundation, an ashram and yoga center.

In this chat, he got candid about his childhood, education, homeschooling, and spirituality. He opened up about his love for motorbikes and golf. 


He takes us through a day in his life and advises us on eating habits we all should follow for healthier living. 


We hope you enjoy watching the video and gain some encouraging advice to lead a healthy and positive life.

snippet.title: #ButtaBomma - Official Trailer | Anikha Surendran,Arjun Das, Surya Vashistta |Gopi Sundar| Shourie T
snippet.description:
The Theatrical Trailer of the Bittersweet Tale of Adolescence and love, #ButtaBomma is here! üíå  In Cinemas 4th Feb 2023!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 09 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 25th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship.

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex‚Äôs wedding but pretending to be the fianc√©e of Istanbul‚Äôs most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS 
From New Line Cinema comes ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods,‚Äù which continues the story of teenage Billy Batson who, upon reciting the magic word ‚ÄúSHAZAM!,‚Äù is transformed into his adult Super Hero alter ego, Shazam. ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods‚Äù stars returning cast members Zachary Levi (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok‚Äù) as Shazam; Asher Angel (‚ÄúAndi Mack‚Äù) as Billy Batson; Jack Dylan Grazer (‚ÄúIt Chapter Two‚Äù) as Freddy Freeman; Adam Brody (‚ÄúPromising Young Woman‚Äù) as Super Hero Freddy; Ross Butler (‚ÄúRaya and the Last Dragon‚Äù) as Super Hero Eugene; Meagan Good (‚ÄúDay Shift‚Äù) as Super Hero Darla; D.J. Cotrona (‚ÄúG.I. Joe: Retaliation‚Äù) as Super Hero Pedro; Grace Caroline Currey (‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation‚Äù) as Mary Bromfield / Super Hero Mary; Faithe Herman (‚ÄúThis Is Us‚Äù) as Darla Dudley; Ian Chen (‚ÄúA Dog‚Äôs Journey‚Äù) as Eugene Choi; Jovan Armand (‚ÄúSecond Chances‚Äù) as Pedro Pena; Marta Milans (‚ÄúWhite Lines‚Äù) as Rosa Vasquez; Cooper Andrews (‚ÄúThe Walking Dead‚Äù) as Victor Vasquez; with Djimon Hounsou (‚ÄúA Quiet Place Part II‚Äù) as Wizard.  Joining the cast are Rachel Zegler (‚ÄúWest Side Story‚Äù), with Lucy Liu (‚ÄúKung Fu Panda‚Äù franchise) and Helen Mirren (‚ÄúF9: The Fast Saga‚Äù).  The film is directed by David F. Tere Bin Episode 11 Teaser - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Episode 3679: Taarak Phas Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha calls from behind, and Taarak turns around to respond, colliding with a passerby and falling into a mud puddle. As a result, his yellow shirt gets stained. Everyone rushes to Taarak's location. Fortunately, he is not injured, but his shirt is ruined. Taarak blames Jetha for the mishap, but the Gokuldham ladies back him up, claiming that he didn't do it on purpose. Taarak will now wear a green shirt because he was unable to obtain another yellow shirt. Champaklal arrives on the scene and decides to support Taarak in front of his boss. Stay tuned to find out how Champaklal saves Taarak from a reprimand from his boss.

The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

localized.description:
Episode 3679: Taarak Phas Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha calls from behind, and Taarak turns around to respond, colliding with a passerby and falling into a mud puddle. As a result, his yellow shirt gets stained. Everyone rushes to Taarak's location. Fortunately, he is not injured, but his shirt is ruined. Taarak blames Jetha for the mishap, but the Gokuldham ladies back him up, claiming that he didn't do it on purpose. Taarak will now wear a green shirt because he was unable to obtain another yellow shirt. Champaklal arrives on the scene and decides to support Taarak in front of his boss. Stay tuned to find out how Champaklal saves Taarak from a reprimand from his boss.

snippet.description:

On Tina's request, Bihaan agrees to marry Sankar. But little does he know that Shraddha is the mastermind behind this plan. She blackmails Tina into saying that she wants Sankar to be her mother. Will Thapki intervene and save Bihaan?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18
snippet.description:
Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18 

The 74th Republic Day Parade was about the spectacular display of made-in-India weapons, increased role of 'Nari Shakti' in the Armed Forces and signs of the country leaving behind its colonial past. For the first time in the history of India‚Äôs Republic Day, the British-era 25-pounder guns, which had been used for decades for the 21-gun salute, were replaced with the indigenous 105mm Indian Field Guns. The vintage artillery, which was once used in the World War II, fell silent and the desi guns boomed for the ceremonial gun salute. Lt Commander Disha Amrith, 29, was the first Navy woman officer to lead a naval contingent of 144 sailors, showcasing the increasing role of 'Nari Shakti' in the military. Armed with assault rifles, women soldiers in colourful uniforms, usually deployed along the desert border with Pakistan, were for the first time joined the BSF camel contingent. Women officers were also part of the contingents of Corps of Signals, Army Air Defence and Army Daredevils

What is Pakistan Economic Crisis?

 Pakistan‚Äôs financial crisis is worsening and the country‚Äôs economy could soon hit rock bottom. In just a matter of three weeks, the South Asian nation‚Äôs inflation has skyrocketed to levels never seen before, and severe food and energy shortages have left over 200 million citizens in huge distress.

A couple of days ago, the world got another glimpse of Pakistan‚Äôs acute financial crisis, as the nation plunged into darkness following its worst power outage in months. The country‚Äôs overburdened electrical system collapsed on January 23, leading to a nationwide blackout that even impacted densely populated cities like Karachi, Islamabad, Lahore and Peshawar.

Are you curious about the current economic crisis in Pakistan? Look no further! Our video provides a thorough analysis of the current economic crisis in Pakistan, discussing the root causes, the impact on the population, and potential solutions. From inflation and unemployment to the devaluation of the rupee and the country's debt crisis, our experts break down the complex issues in a way that is easy to understand. The country‚Äôs overburdened electrical system collapsed on January 23, leading to a nationwide blackout that even impacted densely populated cities like Karachi, Islamabad, Lahore and Peshawar.
